# Browser Preference

When asked to open a URL or perform browser tasks, use **cursor-ide-browser** (built-in Cursor / IDE browser) by default.

Use **user-browsermcp** (external MCP browser) only when:
- The user explicitly asks for the external browser, **user-browsermcp**, the Browser MCP extension, or similar wording that means the external MCP browser, or
- The cursor-ide-browser server is not connected or unavailable (then use user-browsermcp if it is available).
